# for example with the following settings:
# ---
# data -> data
# media -> media
# rise.css -> media/rise.css
# ---
# then once a student has opened slides/01-introduction.ipynb
# then in his working directory there will be
# slides/
#   01-introduction.ipynb
#   data -> /home/jovyan/static/data                 bind-mounted on /nbhosting/static/python-slides/data
#   media -> /home/jovyan/static/media               bind-mounted on /nbhosting/static/python-slides/media
#   rise.css -> /home/jovyan/static/media/rise.css
# ---
# for this course:
rise.css -> media/rise.css 
data -> data
pictures -> pictures
